originalText.text: Lisa has a gift that is truly undeniable. I go to Lisa for all my spiritual readings. My first experience was a tarot card reading which helped me with my life goals and trying to understand the evil eye that my gut was always forewarning me about. Although I did not do the spiritual cleanse because I was missing pertinent information, she gave an excellent rate and answered all my followup questions. All readings are done on the phone and she had very little information about me so some of the things she read blew my mind. The following year I did a full blown psychic reading and the reading was consistent with the last tarot reading just expanded in detail with more relevant info for the present , not just the future. Lisa helped me find all the closure I needed for past pain along with helping me reshift my focus to things that mattered most in my home front and career. I will continue to use Lisa as she even takes me on shorter notice and takes payment with convenient platforms like zelle and venmo

ive seen many psychics and this psychic blew me out of the water. i cannot give details cause it’s personal but i will say that i have spoke to lisa multiple times during the pandemic by phone and all of her predictions came to pass  but also the things she said that she had seen some of it i didnt even mention to my best friend so how exactly did she pick it up ill never fully understand but WOW

all i can say is i highly recommend her. cant wait to speak to her again
